        role="tabpanel"
        class="tab-content border-secondary rounded-box lg:p-6 p-4 prose prose-base max-md:prose-sm min-w-full bg-slate-100 max-xs:!rounded-none"
      >
        <p class="font-bold">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit.
        </p>
        <p>
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Sint tempora
          porro qui temporibus adipisci laborum in nulla accusantium! Eveniet
          provident, voluptate nam quasi molestias nihil sunt sequi nesciunt
          obcaecati quo.
        </p>
